  "title": "A stationary UFO hovered over Sobradinho-DF for 90 min [2002]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/a-stationary-ufo-hovered-over-sobradinho-df-for-90-min-2002/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-j3",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 19th, 2002</strong>. Time: 9:50 am. Duration: 90 minutes. In Sobradinho, a town in the Distrito Federal, two witnesses using binoculars spotted an unidentified flying object with the appearance of a bright star and the shape of a &#8220;balloon&#8221;. The UFO was stationary and at &#8220;very high&#8221; altitude and it remained in this mode for about 90 minutes, leaving no visible trails or trails, according to witnesses who observed it in good visibility conditions and in the &#8220;open sky&#8221;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.629. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário com relato sobre avistamento de Ovni em Sobradinho, Distrito Federal&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
